   <text:p text:style-name="P117"><text:span text:style-name="T19">Raggvaglio</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">dell&apos;origine</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">et giornali successi</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">della gran peste</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Contagiosa, Venefica &amp; Malefica seguita nella Città</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">di Milano &amp; suo Ducato dall&apos;Anno 1629.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">fino all&apos;Anno 1632.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Con le loro </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">successive Provisioni &amp; Ordini.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Aggiuntovi un breve Compendio delle più segnalate specie di Peste</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">in diuersi tempi occorse</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">diviso in dve parti</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Dalla Creatione del Mondo fino alla nascita del Signore,</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Et da N. S. fino alli presenti tempi.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Con diversi antidoti</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> | </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Descritti da</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="smcap1"><text:span text:style-n